RACE.FOOTNOTES: PASS THE CHAMPAGNE was rated off the pace, moved closer with six furlongs to run, drafted inside for most of the turn, shifted to the two path while asked outside the quarter-pole, swung four wide into upper stretch, rallied to the lead coming to the furlong marker and drew away under strong urging. IDIOMATIC showed speed on the inside of a foe, dropped back near the three-quarter pole then tracked outside from that point, made a bid in the three path on the turn, took a short lead into upper stretch, brushed with a rival outside the furlong marker then lost the advantage to the winner and proved no match for the winner while able to get the place. GERRYMANDER showed speed on the outside, moved clear with six furlongs to run, was challenged while in the two path on the turn, came under urging late on that bend, lost the advantage under the crop into upper stretch then drifted out, fought inside of two foes into the final furlong and weakened while clear for the show. TIMELESS JOURNEY settled off the pace, moved closer while shifting from the inside to the three path on the turn and came up empty. KATHLEEN O. was off a couple lengths behind the field while slow into stride, settled at the rear, was urged five wide on the turn, dropped to the three path nearing the quarter-pole and failed to respond in a dull effort. MOMMASGOTTARUN was rated off the pace, came under urging while moving from the two path to the four path on the turn, spun five wide into the stretch and faltered.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: ITSALLCOMINTOGETHA showed the way in hand along the inside, cut the corner and was roused into upper stretch straightened away, edged clear to the eighth pole, dug in under a drive and held safe from a fast closing rival. ONE HEADLIGHT settled just off the inside near the rear of the field, tucked inside with nine-sixteenths to go, came under coaxing at the seven-sixteenths, angled four wide into upper stretch and closed well to just latch on the winner as he hit the wire. DREAMPOINT tracked the pace along the inside coming under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled three to four wide into upper stretch and offered up a mild bid. LOCKE AND KEY chased three to four wide coming under coaxing at the three-eighths, went seven to eight wide into upper stretch and kicked on belatedly to the finish. STOW ON THE WOLD just off the inside tracking the leader in closest aim, came under coaxing three furlongs from home, took the inside route into upper stretch, dug in under a drive but was out-finished in the late stages. THETHRILLOFVICTORY broke in at the start and was corrected, chased three then two wide, offered up a bid taking the inside route into upper stretch, dug in under a drive and was out-finished in the late going. JOINT RESOLUTION chased two to three wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, angled five wide into upper stretch, weakened. LEFTEMBEHIND got bumped at the start by JUST FOR LUCK and was forced to steady conceding four lengths to the front before settling into stride, chased along the inside down the backstretch before tipping two then three wide placed to coaxing at the five-sixteenths, angled six wide into upper stretch and made no impact. ATLANTA'S ACUNA chased along the inside under coaxing from the five-sixteenths, spun just off the inside into upper stretch and weakened. VINCE THE PRINCE tracked from just off the inside just off the pace, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, spun three wide into upper stretch and weakened. JUST FOR LUCK broke out at the start bumping LEFTEMBEHIND, chased along the inside under coaxing from the seven-sixteenths, tipped three wide for home and trailed.
